HSBC Gets License to Open Office in Kenya, Business Daily Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-03-16T04:07:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/hsbc-gets-license-to-open-regional-office-in-kenya-business-daily-reports.html
  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  obtained a
license from the  Central Bank  of  Kenya  to open a regional office
in the East African nation, Business Daily reported, citing Jaap
van Luijk, the bank’s representative in the country.  Further details of the bank’s plans will be announced in
about two weeks, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  